                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2583755/">原教旨托利党人</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-01-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">浅显易懂，非虚构文学的写作典范，文科狗也能读得懂的技术史</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
